snippet.textDisplay: I’ve been thinking about this a lot recently, about how we can properly reward Jurgen for what he has done for the team and the city. He’s German so a Knighthood is out of the question but in keeping with the Royal tradition of rewarding the truly great I wondered whether we should offer him a go on the Queen. I know it’s not conventional but this is fucking Jurgen, and what he’s done for us deserves something special. He may not be interested but if this Royal Family wants to remain relevant in the wake of the Harry/Meghan debacle, it’s the very minimum they could do to make the offer. Interested in your thoughts.

snippet.textDisplay: question for Liverpool FC  and im asking this following question as a lot of fans the Liverpool supporters groups on social media, when Liverpool win the Premier league will the club have the premier league trophy silhouette added to the champions wall at Melwood and the Anfield tunnel, with the premier league being a different shape trophy to the old div 1 trophy, or will they just change the no18 for no19? because when we won a another new trophy that we had never won in our entire history which is the CWC, the silhouette was added next to the super cup, and with the premier league trophy being another brand new trophy that we've never won in our entire history I would have thought they would have also added that silhouette to the walls next to the CWC and put N01 inside it and write premier league trophy underneath it, can you shed any light on whats going to happen regarding this, as a lot of supporters including myself would actually rather see a premier league trophy silhouette added to the wall so that everytime we win it we can change the number in that new trophy, because we all know it would still add up to no19, but would look better to see it as a separate trophy after all they are totally separate trophies and completely different, as the div 1 trophy belongs to the EFL where the premier league trophy does not, especially when you think about the div 1 champions trophy was started and created by and for the FA & the EFL, whereas the premier league trophy was created & the League was  also started  with created with a relegation zone and promotion spots allowed into the new league, which was all created by sky sports
